Can't backtrace to correct mistakes, once you enter the wrong room you won't have the right ingredients and you're stuck, with no advance warning. 3. There's no reset on the puzzles so one misclick (for example the completely nonsensical water puzzle in Mr. Deer's room) and you're stuck. Pity as these are game ruining mistakes you did not make in the free games (played them all and they're awesome!)
